---
title: "Context Lens Session Linking — Corrected Flow (v2)"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant CC as Claude Code<br/>(Main Agent)
    participant Sub as Claude Code<br/>(Subagent)
    participant Plugin as Proxy Plugin<br/>(Claude Adapter)
    participant Proxy as CL Proxy
    participant Store as CL Store

    Note over CC,Store: Startup: Plugin scans ~/.claude/projects/<br/>Builds map: session_UUID → JSONL file ID

    Note over CC,Store: Phase 1: Main agent starts

    CC->>Plugin: POST /v1/messages<br/>metadata.user_id = "...session_AAA"
    Plugin-->>Plugin: Extract session_AAA<br/>Lookup: session_AAA → file_XYZ.jsonl<br/>Set ctx.sessionId = "file_XYZ"
    Plugin->>Proxy: ctx.sessionId = "file_XYZ"
    Proxy->>Store: storeRequest(sessionId="file_XYZ")
    Store-->>Store: sessionId is explicit → skip fingerprint<br/>conv_ID = SHA256("file_XYZ") = conv_777
    Store-->>Store: Create conversation conv_777<br/>Records sessionId: "session_AAA"

    Note over CC,Store: Phase 2: Subagent spawned

    CC->>Sub: Agent tool: "research the codebase"
    Sub->>Plugin: POST /v1/messages<br/>metadata.user_id = "...session_BBB"
    Plugin-->>Plugin: Extract session_BBB<br/>Not in map yet → re-scan JSONL files<br/>Finds session_BBB in file_XYZ.jsonl!<br/>Set ctx.sessionId = "file_XYZ"
    Plugin->>Proxy: ctx.sessionId = "file_XYZ"
    Proxy->>Store: storeRequest(sessionId="file_XYZ")
    Store-->>Store: conv_ID = SHA256("file_XYZ") = conv_777<br/>Same conversation! ✅
    Store-->>Store: Entry added to conv_777<br/>with different agentKey

    Note over CC,Store: Phase 2b: Plugin posts relationship metadata

    Plugin->>Store: POST /api/relationships<br/>{sessionUuid: "session_BBB",<br/>parentUuid: "session_AAA",<br/>type: "child",<br/>agentName: "researcher"}
    Store-->>Store: Resolve session_AAA → conv_777<br/>Store relationship: child agent<br/>within conv_777

    Note over CC,Store: Phase 3: User resumes session (new CLI)

    CC->>Plugin: POST /v1/messages<br/>metadata.user_id = "...session_CCC"
    Plugin-->>Plugin: Extract session_CCC<br/>Re-scan: session_CCC in file_XYZ.jsonl!<br/>Set ctx.sessionId = "file_XYZ"
    Plugin->>Proxy: ctx.sessionId = "file_XYZ"
    Proxy->>Store: storeRequest(sessionId="file_XYZ")
    Store-->>Store: conv_777 already exists ✅<br/>Entry added to same conversation

    Note over CC,Store: Plugin posts continuation relationship
    Plugin->>Store: POST /api/relationships<br/>{sessionUuid: "session_CCC",<br/>parentUuid: "session_AAA",<br/>type: "continuation"}

    Note over CC,Store: Result: All entries in conv_777<br/>with rich relationship metadata<br/>Main → child(researcher) → continuation
